# Mark vendored / auto-generated files so GitHub collapses them in PR diffs
# and excludes them from language stats. See https://github.com/github-linguist/linguist/blob/main/docs/overrides.md

# Vendored from upstream github.com/prometheus/prometheus v0.51.2 — local shim
# module that supplies model/labels and prompb so the agent and grafana/pyroscope
# (which also imports model/labels) don't pull the full prometheus/prometheus
# module dependency tree. Not authored by us; do not review line-by-line.
internal/prom/** linguist-vendored

# Protobuf-generated files (auto-generated by protoc from the .proto definitions
# alongside them). Reviewing them is the same as reviewing the protoc compiler.
internal/prom/prompb/**/*.pb.go linguist-generated
internal/prom/prompb/remote.pb.go linguist-generated
internal/prom/prompb/types.pb.go linguist-generated

# Go module checksum file is machine-managed by `go mod tidy`. Review go.mod
# instead.
go.sum linguist-generated
